    "---\n",
    "## 13. Handle Missing Values Introduced by Lag and Rolling Operations\n",
    "\n",
    "Lag and rolling features naturally introduce missing values at the beginning of each reactor sequence.\n",
    "\n",
    "A naive `dropna()` across the entire dataset is too aggressive because it can remove a large portion of normal operating data.\n",
    "\n",
    "Instead, we use a safer approach:\n",
    "\n",
    "1. remove only the initial lag-affected rows per reactor\n",
    "2. drop remaining missing values only in engineered columns"
   ]
  },
